程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim.examples.power.planetlab

类 MadMmt

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.examples.power.planetlab.MadMmt
public class MadMmt
extends java.lang.Object
A simulation of a heterogeneous power aware data center that applies the Median Absolute Deviation (MAD) VM allocation policy and Minimum Migration Time (MMT) VM selection policy. This example uses a real PlanetLab workload: 20110303. The remaining configuration parameters are in the Constants and PlanetLabConstants classes. If you are using any algorithms, policies or workload included in the power package please cite the following paper: Anton Beloglazov, and Rajkumar Buyya, "Optimal Online Deterministic Algorithms and Adaptive Heuristics for Energy and Performance Efficient Dynamic Consolidation of Virtual Machines in Cloud Data Centers", Concurrency and Computation: Practice and Experience (CCPE), Volume 24, Issue 13, Pages: 1397-1420, John Wiley & Sons, Ltd, New York, USA, 2012
从以下版本开始:
Jan 5, 2012
